<br>
&quot;We have found nothing so far, great Yomen, but it seems that there are several circles of stone columns.  They radiate extremely high amounts of magic, but none of our troops have been able to get to close to them.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Then you will try harder.  There are always more soldiers willing to die for us.  Make them seem worthy and praise them as heroes, I care not.  But we will find he rebels where they hide, and they are to be exterminated with extreme presidence.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Yes, Yomen, I will do as you command.&quot;<br>
